    "description": "<strong>背景故事：</strong><br>在《英灵学院》中，你将穿越时空，踏入一片神秘的次元学院。一个蕴含着古老传说和神秘力量的异界等待着你的探索。在这里，你将遇到来自各种英灵流派的传奇英雄，与他们共同打开次元之门，解开隐藏的秘密。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311260/extras/1c156f28fd8f516c5d8c7f4828eccb7c.poster.avif?t=1746010397\" width=620 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311260/extras/1c156f28fd8f516c5d8c7f4828eccb7c.webm?t=1746010397\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311260/extras/1c156f28fd8f516c5d8c7f4828eccb7c.mp4?t=1746010397\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>模拟经营玩法介绍：</strong><br>成为次元学院的管理者，你将承担起基地的建设与运营。从选择合适的建筑位置，到管理资源、制定发展策略，你需要智慧和耐心来打造一个繁荣的基地。同时，合理分配英灵们的职责，培养他们的技能，以保证基地的稳定运行。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311260/extras/574af64a6d4fd4dee7a91e108e18e572.poster.avif?t=1746010397\" width=620 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311260/extras/574af64a6d4fd4dee7a91e108e18e572.webm?t=1746010397\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311260/extras/574af64a6d4fd4dee7a91e108e18e572.mp4?t=1746010397\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>战斗英灵：</strong><br>战斗英灵有着不同的职业、特点和技能，运用好他们的特性，适当的选择阵容、合理的搭配装备，才能获得比赛的胜利！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311260/extras/ae9397aeb14c644d6bd086e9add2a270.poster.avif?t=1746010397\" width=620 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311260/extras/ae9397aeb14c644d6bd086e9add2a270.webm?t=1746010397\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311260/extras/ae9397aeb14c644d6bd086e9add2a270.mp4?t=1746010397\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>英灵流派介绍：</strong><br>游戏中包括了多种英灵流派，每个流派都有独特组合的技能和特点。拥有不同流派的英灵将带来各种策略组合的可能性，你可以根据自己的喜好和战术偏好来组建强大的队伍，克制各种敌人。从而形成了流派编辑玩法，但在Ban&amp;Pick环节又可能会被打乱节奏。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311260/extras/776ec89792d28ef3e8b0f5fba3b9f0dd.poster.avif?t=1746010397\" width=620 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311260/extras/776ec89792d28ef3e8b0f5fba3b9f0dd.webm?t=1746010397\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311260/extras/776ec89792d28ef3e8b0f5fba3b9f0dd.mp4?t=1746010397\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Ban&amp;Pick玩法介绍：</strong><br>游戏中包括了多种英灵流派，每个流派都有独特组合的技能和特点。拥有不同流派的英灵将带来各种策略组合的可能性，你可以根据自己的喜好和战术偏好来组建强大的队伍，克制各种敌人。从而形成了流派编辑玩法，但在Ban&amp;Pick环节又可能会被打乱节奏。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311260/extras/739bb830dc78ca7a982aedebe7e2c630.poster.avif?t=1746010397\" width=620 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311260/extras/739bb830dc78ca7a982aedebe7e2c630.webm?t=1746010397\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311260/extras/739bb830dc78ca7a982aedebe7e2c630.mp4?t=1746010397\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>赛事进行：</strong><br>依据挑战赛的等级提升，以2v2、3v3和4v4的对战模式，在规定时间内以团队击溃更多的一方获得胜利，战斗中要合理的使用战术会事半功倍！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311260/extras/b2195a1720f1baf9bef10836786a521c.poster.avif?t=1746010397\" width=620 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311260/extras/b2195a1720f1baf9bef10836786a521c.webm?t=1746010397\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311260/extras/b2195a1720f1baf9bef10836786a521c.mp4?t=1746010397\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>总体目标介绍：</strong><br>你的最终目标是解开异界的秘密，掌握隐藏在其中的力量。通过与英灵们的合作，不断探索新的次元，挑战更加强大的敌人，最终成为次元界学院的守护者。<br><br>《英灵学院》是一款独具特色的模拟经营策略游戏，融合了丰富的背景故事和多样化的玩法。通过与英灵们的合作，解锁次元学院的秘密，成为真正的守护者！快来探索这片神秘的异界吧！<br><br>先锋测试玩家评价：<br>●“游戏的背景故事扣人心弦，让我对每一个英灵的传奇故事都感到好奇！”<br>●“模拟经营和ban&amp;pik玩法的结合让游戏充满了战略性，让人乐此不疲。”<br>●“不同流派的英灵让游戏的策略性倍增，每一场战斗都是一次智力的较量。”",
